Class DataTable.TableRowSorter

java.lang.Object
  coffeetable.datastructures.DataTable.TableRowSorter
Enclosing class:
DataTable
static final class DataTable.TableRowSorter
extends java.lang.Object

Private inner class to handle all datatable sorts by calling protected methods inside of DataColumn class. Works by sorting the defined column, receiving a Collection of Map.Entries of record : index, and the sorted order, then reinserting the rows in the sorted order
